#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:462
msgid ""
"A message has been sent to you. See how the button at the bottom of the\n"
"screen has changed appearance? You might now burn this quarry down as it is\n"
"no longer of any use and is just blocking space. To do that, click on the\n"
"quarry and select the destroy button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:610
msgid ""
"A soldier is created as any normal worker: a carrier grabs a tool in a\n"
"warehouse as soon as a request for a certain profession is not fulfilled. "
"The\n"
"tool to create a barbarian soldier is an axe. The newly created soldier is "
"of\n"
"level 0. To make the soldier better in any of the four categories, training "
"is\n"
"needed. Training happens in training sites like the trainings camp or the\n"
"battle arena: soldiers go there (as our little fellows are currently "
"doing),\n"
"consume some wares and advance a level in one category. If a barbarian "
"soldier\n"
"is fully trained, he has level 3 hitpoints, level 5 attack, level 0 defense "
"and\n"
"level 2 evade. This is one fearsome warrior then! The individual statistics\n"
"have the following meaning:"
msgstr ""
"Os soldados recrútanse como calquera traballador: un transportador\n"
"colle un útil nun almacén en canto non se satisfán os requisitos para\n"
"unha profesión concreta. O útil para crear un soldado bárbaro é o\n"
"machado. Os novos soldados teñen nivel cero. Para mellorar aos\n"
"soldados en calquera das catro categorías hai que adestralos. O\n"
"adestramento efectúase en instalacións de adestramento como\n"
"campos de adestramento ou arenas de batalla. Alí van os soldados\n"
"(como fan agora os teus), consumen algúns produtos e avanzan un\n"
"nivel nunha categoría. Se un soldado se adestra completamente,\n"
"terá unha vida de nivel 3, nivel 5 de ataque, cero de defensa e 2 de\n"
"esquivar. Este é un temible soldado! As estatísticas individuais teñen\n"
"o seguinte significado:"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:438
msgid ""
"All windows in Widelands can be closed by right clicking into them. Some\n"
"windows can also be toggled with the buttons at the very bottom of the "
"screen.\n"
"Close the messages window now by right clicking into it."
msgstr ""
"Todas as fiestras en Widelands podes pecharse premendo nelas co botón "
"dereito do rato. Algunhas fiestras poden agocharse mediante os botóns da "
"parte inferior da pantalla do xogo.\n"
"Agora pecha a fiestra de mensaxes premendo nela co botón dereito do rato."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:318
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can directly click the flag where\n"
"the road should end like so."
msgstr ""
"Tamén podes premer directamente na bandeira onde\n"
"vai rematar o camiño."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:266
msgid "And finally the yellow flag symbol only allows for flags."
msgstr ""
"E para rematar, o símbolo da bandeira amarela indica que só se admiten "
"bandeiras."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:412
msgid "Archive all messages in your inbox"
msgstr "Arquivar todas as mensaxes da caixa de entrada"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:407
msgid ""
"Archive all messages, including this one, that you currently have in your\n"
" inbox."
msgstr "Arquivar todas as mensaxes da caixa de entrada, incluída a actual."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:413
msgid "Archive our inbox messages"
msgstr "Arquivas as mensaxes da caixa de entrada"

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:484
msgid ""
"As soon as a military building is manned, it extends your land. You can "
"then\n"
"burn it down again if you need the place. But note that your land is then\n"
"vulnerable: any military site from another player can conquer the land. You\n"
"therefore need military sites to keep military influence over your land."
msgstr ""
"En canto alguén se faga cargo dunha instalación militar, o territorio "
"aumenta.\n"
"Despois podes derrubala se precisas do territorio para construír outro\n"
"edificio. Pero ten en conta que entón o teu territorio será vulnerable. "
"Necesitas\n"
"instalacións militares para manter influencia militar no territorio."

#: ../../campaigns/tutorial01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:682
msgid ""
"Attack and conquer all military buildings of the enemy and destroy its\n"
"headquarters."
msgstr ""
"Ataca e conquista todas as instalacións militares do inimigo e destrúe\n"
"os seus cuarteis."

